@startuml Order Processing Saga - Success Scenario
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Saga-хореография оформления заказа - Успешный сценарий

actor "Покупатель" as Customer
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Event Bus" as EventBus
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Payment Gateway" as PaymentGW
participant "Delivery Service" as Delivery
participant "External Delivery" as ExtDelivery
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Order History Service" as History

Customer -> Order: Оформить заказ
activate Order
Order -> Order: Создать заказ\n(статус: CREATED)
Order -> EventBus: Publish: OrderCreated
deactivate Order

EventBus -> Inventory: OrderCreated
activate Inventory
Inventory -> Inventory: Проверить наличие товаров
Inventory -> Inventory: Зарезервировать товары
Inventory -> EventBus: Publish: InventoryReserved
deactivate Inventory

EventBus -> Payment: InventoryReserved
activate Payment
Payment -> PaymentGW: Запрос на оплату
activate PaymentGW
PaymentGW --> Payment: Оплата успешна
deactivate PaymentGW
Payment -> Payment: Сохранить транзакцию
Payment -> EventBus: Publish: PaymentSucceeded
deactivate Payment

EventBus -> Delivery: PaymentSucceeded
activate Delivery
Delivery -> ExtDelivery: Создать заявку на доставку
activate ExtDelivery
ExtDelivery --> Delivery: Заявка создана, трек-номер
deactivate ExtDelivery
Delivery -> Delivery: Сохранить данные доставки
Delivery -> EventBus: Publish: DeliveryRequestCreated
deactivate Delivery

EventBus -> Notification: DeliveryRequestCreated
activate Notification
Notification -> Notification: Подготовить уведомления
Notification ->> Customer: Отправить уведомление\n(заказ оформлен)
Notification -> EventBus: Publish: CustomerNotificationSent
deactivate Notification

EventBus -> Notification: DeliveryRequestCreated
activate Notification
Notification ->> Order: Отправить уведомление\n(новый заказ)
note right: Продавцу
Notification -> EventBus: Publish: SellerNotificationSent
deactivate Notification

EventBus -> History: OrderCreated,\nInventoryReserved,\nPaymentSucceeded,\nDeliveryRequestCreated
activate History
History -> History: Обновить историю заказа
History -> EventBus: Publish: OrderStatusUpdated\n(статус: IN_DELIVERY)
deactivate History

EventBus -> Order: OrderStatusUpdated
activate Order
Order -> Order: Обновить статус заказа
deactivate Order

Customer -> Order: Проверить статус заказа
activate Order
Order --> Customer: Статус: IN_DELIVERY\nТрек-номер доступен
deactivate Order

@enduml
